final_text: This process has made me more aware of the complexity and nuance in my own beliefs. It’s one thing to hold certain values or ideas abstractly, but being questioned deeply reveals where I might have implicit assumptions or where I haven’t fully worked through contradictions. I’ve found it valuable to articulate and defend my positions clearly, which has strengthened my confidence in some areas while showing me where I might need to be more open to reconsideration. Overall, it’s reinforced for me the importance of ongoing self-reflection and intellectual humility when it comes to understanding myself and the world.
